        "description": "Protected endpoint — two ways to authenticate:\n\n• LOCAL DEV: token variable is already set to 'dev-token-bypass'. Make sure ALLOW_DEV_AUTH_BYPASS=true in your .env. The X-Dev-Uid header carries the uid so the server can find the right user.\n\n• PRODUCTION: Replace the token variable with a real Firebase ID token obtained from the mobile/web client via firebase.auth().currentUser.getIdToken()."
